# Depolarisation

Stimulus ThresholdMosaic
{

    Mode Current
    Pattern Noise
    MeanPercent 120.0
    Variance 0.001
    Delay 0.000000
    Duration 20000
}

StimulusInject ThresholdIntoMosaic
{
    Stimulus ThresholdMosaic
    Target Mosaic
}

